  <entry>
    <title>找到最长的半重复子字符串</title>
    <url>/2023/07/01/%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%80%E9%95%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8A%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%AD%90%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="找到最长的半重复子字符串"><a href="#找到最长的半重复子字符串" class="headerlink" title="找到最长的半重复子字符串"></a><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-the-longest-semi-repetitive-substring/description/">找到最长的半重复子字符串</a></h1><h3 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h3><p>给你一个下标从 <strong>0</strong> 开始的字符串 <code>s</code> ，这个字符串只包含 <code>0</code> 到 <code>9</code> 的数字字符。</p>
<p>如果一个字符串 <code>t</code> 中至多有一对相邻字符是相等的，那么称这个字符串 <code>t</code> 是 <strong>半重复的</strong> 。例如，<code>0010</code> 、<code>002020</code> 、<code>0123</code> 、<code>2002</code> 和 <code>54944</code> 是半重复字符串，而 <code>00101022</code> 和 <code>1101234883</code> 不是。</p>
<p>请你返回 <code>s</code> 中最长 <strong>半重复</strong> 子字符串的长度。一个 <strong>子字符串</strong> 是一个字符串中一段连续 <strong>非空</strong> 的字符。</p>
<h3 id="分析"><a href="#分析" class="headerlink" title="分析"></a>分析</h3><p>题目要求一个字符串中最长的半重复子字符串的长度，很自然的想法是考虑双指针。</p>
<p>我们的右指针不断向前走，并且不断判断当前子字符串是否是<strong>半重复的</strong>，这里可以去维护当前子字符串中<strong>相邻并相同字符对</strong>的个数</p>
<p>只要这样的字符对个数为2时，说明当前子字符串不合法，我们便去移动左指针，移动多少呢？</p>
<p>我们不断移动左指针，使得当前左指针所指位置和其后一个位置的元素相同即可，这样我们可以将该子字符串中的一个<strong>相邻并相同字符对</strong>去掉。</p>
<h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Solution</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">longestSemiRepetitiveSubstring</span>(<span class="params">self, s: <span class="built_in">str</span></span>) -&gt; <span class="built_in">int</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        left=<span class="number">0</span> <span class="comment">#左指针</span></span><br><span class="line">        ans=<span class="number">1</span>  <span class="comment">#最终答案</span></span><br><span class="line">        cnt=<span class="number">0</span>  <span class="comment">#当前子字符串中相邻且相同字符对的个数</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> right <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="built_in">len</span>(s)):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> s[right]==s[right-<span class="number">1</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">                cnt+=<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> cnt&gt;<span class="number">1</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                left+=<span class="number">1</span> <span class="comment">#加1的目的是：从当前子字符串的第2个位置开始判断.</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">while</span> s[left]!=s[left-<span class="number">1</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">                    left+=<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">                cnt=<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            ans=<span class="built_in">max</span>(ans,right-left+<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> ans</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>双指针</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>分割回文串</title>
    <url>/2023/07/01/%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2%E5%9B%9E%E6%96%87%E4%B8%B2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="分割回文串"><a href="#分割回文串" class="headerlink" title="分割回文串"></a><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/palindrome-partitioning/description/">分割回文串</a></h1><h3 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h3><p>给你一个字符串 <code>s</code>，请你将 <code>s</code> 分割成一些子串，使每个子串都是 <strong>回文串</strong> 。返回 <code>s</code> 所有可能的分割方案。</p>
<p><strong>回文串</strong> 是正着读和反着读都一样的字符串。</p>
<h3 id="分析"><a href="#分析" class="headerlink" title="分析"></a>分析</h3><p><code>ans</code>数组去存储最终答案，<code>path</code>数组去存储每一次合法的分割方案.</p>
<p>我们暴力去枚举每种分割方案，在每次分出一个字串的时候去判断其是否为回文串,如果是，加入<code>path</code>, 递归终止时，将<code>path</code> 加入到<code>ans</code>中。</p>
<h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Solution</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">partition</span>(<span class="params">self, s: <span class="built_in">str</span></span>) -&gt; <span class="type">List</span>[<span class="type">List</span>[<span class="built_in">str</span>]]:</span><br><span class="line">        ans=[]</span><br><span class="line">        path=[]</span><br><span class="line">        n=<span class="built_in">len</span>(s)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">dfs</span>(<span class="params">i</span>): <span class="comment">#i是当前字串起始位置</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> i==n:<span class="comment">#递归出口</span></span><br><span class="line">                ans.append(path.copy())</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(i,n): <span class="comment">#j是当前字串的结尾位置</span></span><br><span class="line">                t=s[i:(j+<span class="number">1</span>)]</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> t==t[::-<span class="number">1</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">                    path.append(t)</span><br><span class="line">                    dfs(j+<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                    path.pop()<span class="comment"># 恢复现场</span></span><br><span class="line">        dfs(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> ans</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>回溯</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>求一个整数的惩罚数</title>
    <url>/2023/07/01/%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B4%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%83%A9%E7%BD%9A%E6%95%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="求一个整数的惩罚数"><a href="#求一个整数的惩罚数" class="headerlink" title="求一个整数的惩罚数"></a><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-the-punishment-number-of-an-integer/description/">求一个整数的惩罚数</a></h1><h3 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h3><p>给你一个正整数 <code>n</code> ，请你返回 <code>n</code> 的 <strong>惩罚数</strong> 。</p>
<p><code>n</code> 的 <strong>惩罚数</strong> 定义为所有满足以下条件 <code>i</code> 的数的平方和：</p>
<ul>
<li><code>1 &lt;= i &lt;= n</code></li>
<li><code>i * i</code> 的十进制表示的字符串可以分割成若干连续子字符串，且这些子字符串对应的整数值之和等于 <code>i</code> 。</li>
</ul>
<p>n的范围为1000</p>
<h3 id="分析"><a href="#分析" class="headerlink" title="分析"></a>分析</h3><p>由于n的范围很小，我们可以考虑预处理出每个数的惩罚数是多少，这个问题可以转化为前缀和。</p>
<p>现在问题在于：<strong>如何判断一个数，其满足题目第二个条件</strong>。</p>
<p>显然，我们只能去枚举所有情况，采用的办法为回溯法。</p>
<h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ans=[<span class="number">0</span>]*<span class="number">1001</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">dfs</span>(<span class="params">p,<span class="built_in">sum</span></span>): <span class="comment">#去判断i是否满足第二个条件</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> p==n:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">sum</span>==i</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(p,n):</span><br><span class="line">        x=<span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>.join(s[p:(j+<span class="number">1</span>)]))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> dfs(j+<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="built_in">sum</span>+x):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1001</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    s=<span class="built_in">str</span>(i*i)</span><br><span class="line">    n=<span class="built_in">len</span>(s)</span><br><span class="line">    ans[i]=ans[i-<span class="number">1</span>]+(i*i <span class="keyword">if</span> dfs(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>) <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="number">0</span>)<span class="comment">#前缀和</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Solution</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">punishmentNumber</span>(<span class="params">self, n: <span class="built_in">int</span></span>) -&gt; <span class="built_in">int</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> ans[n]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>回溯</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>统计公平数对的数目</title>
    <url>/2023/07/01/%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3%E6%95%B0%E5%AF%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E7%9B%AE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="统计公平数对的数目"><a href="#统计公平数对的数目" class="headerlink" title="统计公平数对的数目"></a><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/count-the-number-of-fair-pairs/description/">统计公平数对的数目</a></h1><h3 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h3><p>你一个下标从 <strong>0</strong> 开始、长度为 <code>n</code> 的整数数组 <code>nums</code> ，和两个整数 <code>lower</code> 和 <code>upper</code> ，返回 <strong>公平数对的数目</strong> 。</p>
<p>如果 <code>(i, j)</code> 数对满足以下情况，则认为它是一个 <strong>公平数对</strong> ：</p>
<ul>
<li><code>0 &lt;= i &lt; j &lt; n</code></li>
<li><code>lower &lt;= nums[i] + nums[j] &lt;= upper</code></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="分析"><a href="#分析" class="headerlink" title="分析"></a>分析</h3><p>显然，我们将数组排序后再去考虑这个问题与原问题是一样的。</p>
<p>对于一个固定的<code>nums[i]</code>,则 <code>nums[j]</code> 的范围为: $[lower-nums[i],upper-nums[i]]$ </p>
<p>也就是说，我们只需要去求数组中，范围在$[lower-nums[i],upper-nums[i]]$ 中的数的个数$k$。</p>
<p>然后我们有：$k=$ 小于等于$upper-nums[i]$ 的数的个数 $-$ 小于 $lower-nums[i]$ 的数的个数 </p>
<ul>
<li>小于等于$upper-nums[i]$ 的数的个数 $=$ 第一个大于$upper-nums[i]$ 的数的下标</li>
<li>小于$lower-nums[i]$ 的数的个数 $=$   第一个大于$lower-nums[i]$ 的数的下标</li>
</ul>
<p>注意：为了避免重复计算，上述所有所有的数均在范围$[0,i-1]$ 中去找。</p>
<h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Solution</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">countFairPairs</span>(<span class="params">self, nums: <span class="type">List</span>[<span class="built_in">int</span>], lower: <span class="built_in">int</span>, upper: <span class="built_in">int</span></span>) -&gt; <span class="built_in">int</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        ans=<span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">        nums.sort()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> j,x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">enumerate</span>(nums):</span><br><span class="line">            r=bisect_right(nums,upper-x,<span class="number">0</span>,j)</span><br><span class="line">            l=bisect_left(nums,lower-x,<span class="number">0</span>,j)</span><br><span class="line">            ans+=r-l</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> ans</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>二分</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>英语每日练3——金融新闻</title>
    <url>/2023/07/01/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E7%BB%833%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>It was another mostly mixed session for stocks.  The S&amp;P managed to close at a record high again.  The Dow rose 57 points to close just shy of a new high.  Federal Reserve chair J. Powell spoke at the IMF seminar earlier on a panel hosted by Sara Eisen.  Once again he struck a decidedly dovish tone, giving no hint of contemplating any rate hike any time soon.  Powell said the economic recovery remains incomplete and uneven.  Investors cheered the continued easy-money mindset from the Fed.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="翻译"><a href="#翻译" class="headerlink" title="翻译"></a>翻译</h3><blockquote>
<p> 这又是一个涨跌互现的交易日。标准普尔500指数再次创下历史新高。道琼斯工业平均指数上升57点，接近新高。美联储主席鲍威尔早些时候在由萨拉·艾森主持的国际货币基金组织研讨会上发表了讲话。他再次坚定地采取鸽派语气，没有暗示近期会考虑加息。鲍威尔说，经济复苏仍然不完整和不平衡。投资者为美联储继续保持宽松货币政策的心态而欢呼。</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="知识点"><a href="#知识点" class="headerlink" title="知识点"></a>知识点</h3><ul>
<li>mixed: 涨跌参半</li>
<li>session：交易日</li>
<li>manage to do： 成功做</li>
<li>just shy of： 差点</li>
<li>Federal Reserve： 美联储</li>
<li>seminar： 研讨会</li>
<li>panel：专家小组</li>
<li>decidedly: 坚定地</li>
<li>dovish： 鸽派的</li>
<li>give no hint of：没有任何暗示</li>
<li>contemplate： 考虑</li>
<li>uneven： 不平衡的</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>英语每日练</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
