    <title>英语每日练4——金融新闻</title>
    <url>/2023/07/02/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E7%BB%834%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>CVS is also jumping on better-than-expected quarterly earnings ,with the drugstore operator also raising its full-year forecast. CVS results were helped by the performance from its insurance unit as well as strong sales of over-the-counter COVID-19 tests.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="翻译"><a href="#翻译" class="headerlink" title="翻译"></a>翻译</h3><blockquote>
<p> 药店运营商CVS也因季度收益好于预期而大幅上涨，该公司也上调了全年预期。CVS的业绩得益于其保险部门的表现以及非处方COVID-19检测产品的强劲销售。</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="知识点"><a href="#知识点" class="headerlink" title="知识点"></a>知识点</h3><ul>
<li>jump on：因……上涨</li>
<li>over-the-counter: 非处方的.、</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
